    "title": "Clinical Pulmonary Infection Score (CPIS) for Ventilator-Associated Pneumonia (VAP)",
    "desc": "The Clinical Pulmonary Infection Score (CPIS) assists in diagnosing ventilator-associated pneumonia (VAP) by predicting benefit of pulmonary cultures.",
    "data": {
        "orgreference": [
